videos.headline: Stanford extends lead with 40-yard TD pass
videos.description: Stanford QB Ryan Burns finds a wide open Michael Rector for a 40-yard touchdown reception to put Stanford up 10-0 over Kansas State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Stanford extends lead with 40-yard TD pass) 2016/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: McCaffrey dazzles rushing 35 yards for first TD of season
videos.description: Christian McCaffrey side steps away from a defender and breaks free for a 35-yard touchdown run, giving him his first score of the season and extending Stanford's lead over Kansas State.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (McCaffrey dazzles rushing 35 yards for first TD of season) 2016/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: McCaffrey bursts through hole for second TD
videos.description: Christian McCaffrey finds a gap and races down the field 41 yards for his second touchdown of the game to extend Stanford's lead over Kansas State to 26-13.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (McCaffrey bursts through hole for second TD) 2016/09/02 ESHEET

videos.headline: McCaffrey's two TDs lead Stanford to win
videos.description: Christian McCaffrey's Heisman hopes are off to a good start, rushing for two touchdowns on 126 yards in Stanford's 26-13 win over Kansas State.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCF Interview (McCaffrey's two TDs lead Stanford to win) 2016/9/2 ESHEET
